name: ''my gyoza''
description: A work by Mical Noelson. ’’my gyoza’’ is a conceptual work born out of the desire to reign in the anxiety related to promoting my work on social media. The price is purposefully prohibitive as part of the concept. The price of the work in no way indicates it’s future price or the price floor of any of my art. This work might end up having a a companion piece called ‘’my salsa ingredients’’.
